{"tid":301878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTGF: 我唔係雞，我只係做社工","createTime":"2017-06-29T03:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T21:27:19.000Z","uid":34503,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4beffab8b8bae3c7d03a63b0ae11eaaabe9f8c16","tid":301878,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:25:45.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong&rsquo;s part-time girlfriends (and a boyfriend) tell their stories<br />\n<br />\nA 16-year-old who feels compelled to sell her companionship, though not her body, to earn money, a 26-year-old who sounds like a life coach - women shrug off the stigma of being girlfriends for hire, and the frequent requests for sex<br />\n<br />\nJessica LiUPDATED :&nbsp;Wednesday, 28 Jun 2017, 7:12PM<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;36<br />\n<br />\nJo, a 16-year-old Hong Kong student, opened an Instagram account in May to offer her services as a part-time girlfriend. She&rsquo;s trying to save HK$40,000 to buy a clarinet, she says, and made HK$3,000 in her first month. Jo meets clients, aged between 25 and 35, about twice a week at nighttime and during weekends, when she&rsquo;s not studying.<br />\n<br />\nThe phenomenon of part-time girlfriends &ndash; or PTGFs &ndash; for rent in Hong Kong has blossomed on social media in recent months. They offer services ranging from dining out to watching movies, but also the full gamut of sexual services, with dates costing between HK$100 and HK$4,000, depending on what&rsquo;s on the agenda.<br />\n<br />\nThe trend made headlines last week when 10 Hong Kong women, including a secondary school pupil, were arrested on suspicion of advertising sexual services as part-time girlfriends on their Instagram and Facebook accounts.<br />\n<br />\nRead more: <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/2100125/hong-kong-part-time-girlfriends-and-boyfriend-tell-their-stories-why-they\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.scmp.com%2Flifestyle%2Farticle%2F2100125%2Fhong-kong-part-time-girlfriends-and-boyfriend-tell-their-stories-why-they&d=O6IRHH6heEBx9e2wK3qu4YsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=f014eb5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/2100125/hong-kong-part-time-girlfriends-and-boyfriend-tell-their-stories-why-they</a>"},{"pid":"f385076410f21ea6b3a610b11084b7c2450614c5","tid":301878,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"收錢既社工？"},{"pid":"152d94a81762781511e76b3e4e5d70e48e3274a0","tid":301878,"uid":121711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"社工，全部都係社工"},{"pid":"c40b5d32ed8053b57190ec42af08f3a33b4ed81f","tid":301878,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"啱呀，收社工價錢，賤過雞"},{"pid":"382f4be12e7f980e59eccde19ba7fa324858be42","tid":301878,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c834409ab52054de1bd09857a6ad4fbbc8f68f74","tid":301878,"uid":83819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963de080045c401ab411a4ea2c2aaf34c04ac081","tid":301878,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"需要社工輔導"},{"pid":"610c66679e049c1964de8eba3e5cb44c97157bff","tid":301878,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b79c7e4ca0919dd6c3f1c0b02259fb71a14e3d","tid":301878,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收錢既社工？</blockquote><br />\n有社工唔收錢？"},{"pid":"e3b1a91cbb9e874324cc6e24ec7555e60c7264ac","tid":301878,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"